{"tid":2242528,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲少女管白電油原判感化　律政司上訴得直改判","createTime":"2020-10-14T05:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T05:52:38.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5218a7d5e46390da5c5f9b7a4d67befac7d2b9a5","tid":2242528,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名15歲少女於去年被搜出管有白電油等，被判一年感化令，律政司申請刑期覆核得直，改判120小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n15歲女被告於去年國慶前夕在天水圍遭警員截查，被搜出白電油及含乙醇殘留物的玻璃樽等，早前承認管有工具意圖作非法用途罪，被判一年感化令。<br />\n<br />\n律政司不滿刑罰過輕，申請刑期覆核。上訴庭首席法官潘兆初指，考慮到被告社會服務令報告，認為判以社會服務令是合適的刑罰，改判被告120小時社會服務令及遵守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=408985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408985&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2l95pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=eee25668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408985&h=8cae9fde\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=408985</a>"},{"pid":"5d5ba5bfe22957d40252ee07133390e74e4e7af9","tid":2242528,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"都係唔駛坐喎，咁駛唔駛再上訴呀大波華？"},{"pid":"16a026b9d0ef994674893508415a5971ae5b2bd6","tid":2242528,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"白電油去污漬幾好用，有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n化學老師都成日係電台教人用呢招清潔架啦"},{"pid":"47aaa32d8732a8baa2fc91b679e14bc800f0e752","tid":2242528,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"Zippo 火機"}]}